{"tid":1434772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[[[全部記者同我入晒黎]]]今日四點記者會","createTime":"2019-08-09T01:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T04:21:51.000Z","uid":6375,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7f2e0161ac30a0a84556650393ace1f3d7061a14","tid":1434772,"uid":6375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:06:37.000Z","msg":"我係一位抗爭者<br />\n但我睇到狗隻對記者所做嘅野<br />\n實在無辦法再忍落去<br />\n點都要阻止佢地<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n好似前幾日咁樣<br />\n狗開波前 發表意見 非常好<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日記招對策</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 啊sir一入黎，全部用強光電筒照向佢地，直至完場</span></span><br />\n記住唔好用手機個led，唔夠勁架<br />\n佢哋口口聲聲話laser對佢哋眼睛受傷，唔通記者俾你啲大光燈照就唔傷咩？<br />\n其實傻嘅都知佢地有咩企圖<br />\n每次拉左人，之後記者圍住黎影，佢地係一定開燈照<br />\n佢地唔想俾人影到，唔想俾人睇到<br />\n佢地唔想七警案再發生<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日一於照足佢一整場記招，睇下佢傷唔傷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 每個記者都問致命問題 </span></span><br />\n大家琴日有目共睹，一問過期催淚彈，就淆撚到仆街<br />\n所以，今日每個記者都以過期催淚彈問題為第一條問題，問撚到佢答為止<br />\n全世界要用追問幾次先至好pass俾下一位記者<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">條死閪婆MC一定阻你地(例如:江sir頭先答左架喇)，你地一定要合作，屌鳩番條閪婆，唔好俾到壓倒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記者們你地要加油，繼續為香港記錄事實真相<br />\n已經有利君雅<ins><strong>被消失</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>香港人需要你們</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps: 請幫手share俾記者 記協"},{"pid":"960629db165530a080553165ecaf75c38788daaa","tid":1434772,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:08:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"081604eb2d01153b72fc188fee486a455b392f9a","tid":1434772,"uid":31174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:08:22.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"c8df8d526b03ef18f8fd21edac41dfe3f3de6da3","tid":1434772,"uid":22011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:08:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4383a465d5faeebd6aec9390a0b1fd263f412ce","tid":1434772,"uid":251292,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:09:44.000Z","msg":"求求立場記者唔好再玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣只會弱化左成個記者會記者點樣狙擊班狗答都答唔到"},{"pid":"29a788ffa1c2db51ba764d54dd8096756a275809","tid":1434772,"uid":65556,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:09:45.000Z","msg":"巴打update下資訊先<br />\nRTHK出咗聲明澄清利君雅無被消失"},{"pid":"e8bcd8a4cb2964f93136a8e2ce185a5066fe5440","tid":1434772,"uid":251292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4383a465d5faeebd6aec9390a0b1fd263f412ce","tid":1434772,"uid":251292,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:09:44.000Z","msg":"求求立場記者唔好再玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣只會弱化左成個記者會記者點樣狙擊班狗答都答唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:10:16.000Z","msg":"I mean ig個幾個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2188da5450c25aa81c28c5199591398ff460a4","tid":1434772,"uid":224402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4383a465d5faeebd6aec9390a0b1fd263f412ce","tid":1434772,"uid":251292,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:09:44.000Z","msg":"求求立場記者唔好再玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣只會弱化左成個記者會記者點樣狙擊班狗答都答唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:11:16.000Z","msg":"無聽，點玩？"},{"pid":"b49a74f6d1591a16d42eadad303bad9f366b06d3","tid":1434772,"uid":6375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29a788ffa1c2db51ba764d54dd8096756a275809","tid":1434772,"uid":65556,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:09:45.000Z","msg":"巴打update下資訊先<br />\nRTHK出咗聲明澄清利君雅無被消失"}